items.title: Unicode collation algorithm - Wikipedia, the free encyclopedia
items.htmlTitle: Unicode collation algorithm - Wikipedia, the free encyclopedia
items.snippet:
The Unicode collation algorithm (UCA) is an algorithm defined in Unicode 
Technical Report #10, which defines a customizable method to compare two 
strings.
